{"tid":2205807,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有熱愛社會 案例啦","createTime":"2020-09-17T05:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T05:54:03.000Z","uid":33373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82bef38aa161ee13858ab1fd5cd147aab8eebf0c","tid":2205807,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"老翁認刺長毛 稱許智峯黃之鋒遲早要死 官讚熱愛社會准保釋候判<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n八旬老翁今年4月16日在中聯辦外以金屬尖鑿刺向「長毛」梁國雄腰窩，聲稱要替天行道，被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。案件原定今早開審，但老翁在開審前認罪，惟他強調自己是為「香港出頭」，又謂「我係為大家好，唔係為自己」，更揚言「一個許智峯，一個黃之鋒，兩個遲早都要死」。雖則如此，裁判官鄭紀航仍指老翁熱愛社會，只因政見不同而犯案，遂先為老翁索取社會服務令報告，押後至下月13日判刑，其間老翁更可繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老翁認刺長毛 稱許智峯黃之鋒遲早要死 官讚熱愛社會准保釋候判<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/WLVRWY7A7BERRKFZI2KYRPWO4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FWLVRWY7A7BERRKFZI2KYRPWO4I%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BhqcspSF5fyAY0%2FEGx5AO9c%3D&h=c4b2c1c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FWLVRWY7A7BERRKFZI2KYRPWO4I%2F&h=f386edf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/WLVRWY7A7BERRKFZI2KYRPWO4I/</a>"},{"pid":"f75255301ef48548ec6921fd3c7fd82c9873c90d","tid":2205807,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>法官鼓勵傷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"eb5474c745c82f900e3d9127aeb5831d786378e1","tid":2205807,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"ok"}]}